# Claude Code Skills Directory

This directory contains project-specific skills for Claude Code. Skills are reusable workflows and processes that guide Claude's behavior for specific tasks.

## Directory Structure

Each skill follows this structure:

```
.claude/skills/
├── skill-name/
│   ├── SKILL.md          (required - the skill definition)
│   ├── reference.md      (optional - additional documentation)
│   ├── examples.md       (optional - usage examples)
│   ├── scripts/          (optional - helper utilities)
│   │   └── helper.py
│   └── templates/        (optional - file templates)
│       └── template.txt
└── CLAUDE.md             (this file - directory documentation)
```

